### Register
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123"
}

### Login — скопируй accessToken из ответа
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "StrongPass123"
}

